{"id": 483, "genre": 1001, "title": "人们对你的工作地点有什么常见误解？", "description": "在景阳冈的，除了武松还有老虎呢。", "record_count": 1657, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160606145041KFlG8ewBipT0X7Ij.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-08-19T14:46:24Z", "options": [{"id": 8704, "content": "谁说物流行业就一定要做快递啊？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166510}, {"id": 8450, "content": "广告公司？就是设计海报吧？", "image": null, "praise_count": 73, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163981}, {"id": 8451, "content": "我们公司叫能力有限公司，行不", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 124369}, {"id": 8453, "content": "在牛排餐厅上班就一定要会煎牛排？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164012}, {"id": 8454, "content": "大学学经济类专业就能炒股", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162247}, {"id": 8455, "content": "国贸三上班的公关，不是正当行业吧？", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164041}, {"id": 8456, "content": "做工程的，身上应该有土，皮肤还黑??", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164069}, {"id": 8458, "content": "在软件园上班的都是程序员。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137140}, {"id": 8461, "content": "医院里除了医生就是护士", "image": null, "praise_count": 66, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164152}, {"id": 8463, "content": "国外留学回来的吧？来来来刚刚电视那女的讲了什么/帮我翻译这份文件。", "image": null, "praise_count": 99, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164174}, {"id": 8465, "content": "供电局上班容易被以为是收电费", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164028}, {"id": 8466, "content": "忙的忙死 闲的闲死", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164207}, {"id": 8978, "content": "山东的？ 肯定会开挖掘机吧!", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143221}, {"id": 8467, "content": "铁路工作，你一定能买到票", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 59573}, {"id": 8468, "content": "都以为在地下工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164207}, {"id": 10517, "content": "洗足店按摩店高级会所一定是那种地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 176352}, {"id": 8474, "content": "好好笑啊?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 39258}, {"id": 8730, "content": "夜店工作就一定是坐台女?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166020}, {"id": 8476, "content": "什么，公关行业？小姑娘挺漂亮的呀?怎么收费？", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 66079}, {"id": 8479, "content": "在保险公司工作、就是卖保险的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164294}, {"id": 8743, "content": "建筑设计啊？那你给我家看看装修。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167011}, {"id": 8489, "content": "在学校上班？哦哦哦，老师啊。我在学校看大门不行吗( ˉ ⌓ ˉཀ๑)", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164346}, {"id": 7978, "content": "什么，在中关村你还不会修电脑？", "image": null, "praise_count": 181, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 7979, "content": "后海上班你一定是酒吧歌手吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 7980, "content": "陆家嘴工作，金融精英啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 110, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 10028, "content": "科技大学就是蓝领！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157295}, {"id": 8749, "content": "学舞蹈的？跳一段吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166990}, {"id": 8496, "content": "做广告的啊？一定会做灯箱！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164394}, {"id": 8497, "content": "主题公园上班就是享福了", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234908EuDZCpeQKlNs2Bog.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163734}, {"id": 8498, "content": "在网吧工作", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234957jKLZE2YboQ8MkyOV.jpg", "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164424}, {"id": 8509, "content": "上外语学校你出来只能当翻译（只是学校叫这个名字好么）", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164448}, {"id": 8765, "content": "社会工作混社会吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 81059}, {"id": 8510, "content": "公关公司？哎呀 挺好一个小伙子…怎么", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164452}, {"id": 8511, "content": "广告公司的？你说做电视广告？还是报纸广告...?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146366}, {"id": 8512, "content": "啊！你在中石油上班？那你开车加油是不是不用花钱啊？有没有油卡给兄弟几张！", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145791}, {"id": 8517, "content": "哪怕巴菲特，只要四平方就足够了！天朝爱装，卖包子的也要买个大班台！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163972}, {"id": 8519, "content": "哦，人力资源啊，那不就是行政么，什么？搞人事哒，那肯定就是人精啊，就心眼儿都少不了吧～", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163750}, {"id": 8522, "content": "在某移动运营总部上班。哦，你们营业厅累不累，都说了是总部。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163487}, {"id": 8523, "content": "在银行上班？工资一定很高吧~", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164690}, {"id": 8779, "content": "车辆工程？那你会修车吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145581}, {"id": 8524, "content": "在猎头公司工作？那你帮我找份工作～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164700}, {"id": 8781, "content": "服装专业？帮我设计个衣服呗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167406}, {"id": 8526, "content": "我在运营商工作，那你每天都没事做啦，工资又高", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164762}, {"id": 8527, "content": "教老外中文？那有什么专业性可言啊？会说普通话和英语的不都可以教么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163609}, {"id": 8787, "content": "蓝翔就只能有教挖掘机的吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167393}, {"id": 8790, "content": "武装部就是负责打仗的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167506}, {"id": 8540, "content": "电通？是电力公司还是电信公司？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145545}, {"id": 8541, "content": "“在哪儿混呢”\n“俄罗斯”\n“那你肯定抗冻阿”", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164273}, {"id": 8555, "content": "呀，你学旅游规划与设计的，毕业做导游的呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164987}, {"id": 8557, "content": "—每天看很多走私货吧？\n—不，那是海关我是海事。\n—哦，那要去钓鱼岛和日本船对峙吧？\n—不，那是海警我是海事。\n—噢，海上那么多小渔船很难管吧？\n—不，那是渔政我是海事。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164986}]}